description: Try our easy to follow Seafood Pizza recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Seafood pizza,Quick & easy dinner,High fibre,High protein,Low sugar,Easter
name: Seafood Pizza Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Place pizza bases onto baking trays. Spread each with tomato paste and sprinkle with mozzarella. Bake in preheated oven for 5 minutes or until heated through.

Combine marinara, garlic and parsley. Arrange over pizza bases with tomato. Drizzle with oil and season with salt and pepper. Bake in oven for a further 8 minutes or until seafood is cooked. Remove from oven and cut into wedges. Serve with rocket.
